---
title: Portuguese-Style Chicken Burger with Fries & Garlic Aioli
description: These burgers are jam-packed with delicious flavours, from the juicy Portuguese-style chicken to the creamy lemon aioli and sweet caramelised onion. You'll never settle for a takeaway burger again!
